# Machine Configuration
# Copy this file to CONFIG.md (gitignored) and fill in your values,
# or run /configure to auto-detect everything.

## Hardware
- GPU: <gpu name, e.g. NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5090>, <vram> GB VRAM
- Storage: <free> TB free at <models_root>

## Paths
- Models root: <absolute path, e.g. /mnt/data/models>
- llama binaries: <bin dir, e.g. ~/.local/bin> (llama-bench, llama-cli, llama-server, llama-mtmd-cli, llama-gguf-split)
- llama.cpp repo: <path to llama.cpp source, e.g. ~/code/llama.cpp>
- Python venv: <venv path, e.g. /mnt/data/models/.venv> (huggingface_hub, hf CLI — no pip)
- System python3: also has huggingface_hub <version>
